WEBVTT

00:00:02.002 --> 00:00:04.379
WRITTEN BY HYUGA NATSU

00:01:32.091 --> 00:01:33.509
{\an8}THIS STORY IS A FICTION AND ALL NAMES OF
FIGURES AND ORGANIZATIONS ARE FICTITIOUS.

00:01:33.510 --> 00:01:34.719
{\an8}MOREOVER, THE STORY HAS NO RELATION
TO REAL-LIFE INCIDENTS AND EVENTS.

00:01:40.892 --> 00:01:41.810
Suirei.

00:01:46.022 --> 00:01:49.233
At least keep the rats under control.

00:01:49.234 --> 00:01:50.819
I'm terribly sorry.

00:01:51.653 --> 00:01:52.612
Oh?

00:01:53.738 --> 00:01:55.907
<i>I've seen this child before.</i>

00:01:57.492 --> 00:01:59.159
Lady Shenmei.

00:01:59.160 --> 00:02:00.661
I apologize.

00:02:00.662 --> 00:02:03.206
He is Shirou's child.

00:02:04.624 --> 00:02:06.292
Just a child's prank.

00:02:11.923 --> 00:02:13.299
Come on, let's go.

00:02:14.008 --> 00:02:14.926
Mother.

00:02:15.718 --> 00:02:17.053
Loulan.

00:02:19.430 --> 00:02:22.224
<i>I knew it!</i>

00:02:22.225 --> 00:02:26.771
Well, then, whip this girl.

00:02:27.438 --> 00:02:30.149
A hundred lashes should be enough.

00:02:30.150 --> 00:02:32.818
Prepare a pillar to tie her to.

00:02:32.819 --> 00:02:34.237
Lady Shenmei, please.

00:02:38.867 --> 00:02:40.325
<i>This is bad.</i>

00:02:40.326 --> 00:02:43.663
<i>That woman's dangerous. I sneaked in</i>

00:02:44.247 --> 00:02:45.415
<i>and saw the Feifa.</i>

00:02:46.124 --> 00:02:48.625
<i>They'll claim it's punishment
and get rid of me.</i>

00:02:48.626 --> 00:02:50.294
Hurry up.

00:02:50.295 --> 00:02:51.379
Mother,

00:02:52.005 --> 00:02:54.006
remember what you said before?

00:02:54.007 --> 00:02:56.425
That you wanted a new apothecary?

00:02:56.426 --> 00:02:58.094
This girl is it.

00:03:01.431 --> 00:03:03.724
She doesn't look like one.

00:03:03.725 --> 00:03:07.562
True, but she's over 30.

00:03:09.898 --> 00:03:12.482
By constantly testing her own medicines,

00:03:12.483 --> 00:03:14.485
she's made her body stop aging.

00:03:15.278 --> 00:03:16.486
Oh?

00:03:16.487 --> 00:03:19.281
I do not know which medicine works,

00:03:19.282 --> 00:03:22.869
but she may be able to
create an elixir of immortality.

00:03:23.578 --> 00:03:26.997
If she fails,
she'll die like the man before her.

00:03:26.998 --> 00:03:29.626
<i>An elixir of immortality?
The man before her?</i>

00:03:30.251 --> 00:03:33.128
Well, if that's the case, then fine.

00:03:33.129 --> 00:03:36.382
Lady Ayla,
we'll continue this conversation later.

00:03:37.258 --> 00:03:38.092
Yeah.

00:03:41.763 --> 00:03:42.972
Oh, right.

00:03:43.806 --> 00:03:46.476
She won't be able to work here properly, right?

00:03:47.393 --> 00:03:49.729
Take the apothecary with us,

00:03:50.521 --> 00:03:52.649
to our "Fortress."

00:03:57.695 --> 00:03:59.447
<i>So Shisui's true identity was</i>

00:04:00.031 --> 00:04:01.407
<i>Consort Loulan.</i>

00:04:02.283 --> 00:04:03.576
<i>What an actress.</i>

00:04:04.160 --> 00:04:06.579
<i>No, more like a tanuki.</i>

00:04:07.705 --> 00:04:10.040
<i>When I gave special lessons
to the four ladies,</i>

00:04:10.041 --> 00:04:14.295
<i>she sat there
in flashy clothes, expressionless.</i>

00:04:15.171 --> 00:04:17.130
<i>She avoided the Empress Dowager</i>

00:04:17.131 --> 00:04:20.093
<i>and didn't get near
Consort Lishu in the bath,</i>

00:04:20.677 --> 00:04:23.846
<i>probably so no one would realize
she was Consort Loulan.</i>

00:04:24.847 --> 00:04:26.848
<i>She did not hide from me,</i>

00:04:26.849 --> 00:04:29.101
<i>because when I caught Maomao,</i>

00:04:29.102 --> 00:04:31.396
<i>I didn't recognize her as Consort Loulan.</i>

00:04:32.355 --> 00:04:34.440
<i>I had a vague feeling though.</i>

00:04:34.983 --> 00:04:38.235
<i>She liked bugs, was a little odd,</i>

00:04:38.236 --> 00:04:41.239
<i>and gossiped like any normal girl.</i>

00:04:42.907 --> 00:04:46.703
<i>Turns out I was completely fooled.</i>

00:04:54.961 --> 00:04:57.297
This was the room
used by the previous apothecary.

00:05:02.635 --> 00:05:05.930
I didn't plan to bring you this far.

00:05:07.181 --> 00:05:08.474
Is Shisui

00:05:08.975 --> 00:05:11.269
your half-sister?

00:05:12.687 --> 00:05:16.815
She's the only one
who treats me like a sister.

00:05:16.816 --> 00:05:17.859
<i>I thought so.</i>

00:05:18.985 --> 00:05:22.279
<i>I heard Loulan was
Lord Shishou's only daughter,</i>

00:05:22.280 --> 00:05:25.366
<i>but if there was a second daughter
from another mother,</i>

00:05:26.242 --> 00:05:28.952
<i>then someone
as terrifying as Lady Shenmei,</i>

00:05:28.953 --> 00:05:30.872
<i>would never approve of her existence.</i>

00:05:31.873 --> 00:05:35.960
Lady Shenmei absolutely despises me.

00:05:37.003 --> 00:05:39.254
<i>My father, Shishou,</i>

00:05:39.255 --> 00:05:41.841
<i>was just a branch member
of the Shi family.</i>

00:05:42.383 --> 00:05:44.552
<i>But due to his talents,</i>

00:05:45.053 --> 00:05:47.555
<i>he was adopted into the main family,
Lady Shenmei's family.</i>

00:05:48.264 --> 00:05:50.599
<i>That's when he was given
the name "Shishou,"</i>

00:05:50.600 --> 00:05:52.435
<i>and the two got engaged.</i>

00:05:53.352 --> 00:05:54.853
<i>But during the previous emperor's reign,</i>

00:05:54.854 --> 00:05:57.440
<i>Lady Shenmei was summoned
to the rear palace.</i>

00:05:58.274 --> 00:06:01.235
<i>When she returned years later,
supposedly as a gift,</i>

00:06:02.278 --> 00:06:04.989
<i>my mother and I
were already at my father's side.</i>

00:06:05.907 --> 00:06:09.534
<i>She kicked us out of the house</i>

00:06:09.535 --> 00:06:11.579
<i>and made us work as servants.</i>

00:06:12.288 --> 00:06:14.414
<i>She even hated the fact</i>

00:06:14.415 --> 00:06:18.252
<i>that my name included a character
from the Shi family.</i>

00:06:19.087 --> 00:06:21.172
Wait, then "Shisui".

00:06:22.423 --> 00:06:25.550
Yeah. That used to be my name.

00:06:25.551 --> 00:06:28.429
Seems like Loulan really liked that name.

00:06:29.138 --> 00:06:31.264
<i>If she was going to use
a fake name as a maid,</i>

00:06:31.265 --> 00:06:33.893
<i>she could have picked something else.</i>

00:06:36.687 --> 00:06:38.356
That's just how she is.

00:06:39.816 --> 00:06:44.362
<i>Born from the same father
but different mothers.</i>

00:06:45.113 --> 00:06:50.243
{\an8}<i>One raised like a flower,
offered to the emperor.</i>

00:06:50.910 --> 00:06:52.744
<i>The other,</i>

00:06:52.745 --> 00:06:54.871
<i>sent to the rear palace
as just a handmaid,</i>

00:06:54.872 --> 00:06:56.207
<i>moving in the shadows.</i>

00:06:58.751 --> 00:07:01.461
<i>Suirei was involved in
the attempted assassination of Lord Jinshi</i>

00:07:01.462 --> 00:07:03.214
<i>at the middle shrine.</i>

00:07:04.590 --> 00:07:07.050
<i>She used the chaos
of the warehouse explosion</i>

00:07:07.051 --> 00:07:08.552
<i>to steal the ritual tools,</i>

00:07:08.553 --> 00:07:11.222
<i>and when it was discovered,
she faked her death and escaped.</i>

00:07:12.265 --> 00:07:15.601
<i>And the recent Feifa attack...</i>

00:07:16.269 --> 00:07:18.688
<i>Lord Shishou was probably behind that too.</i>

00:07:19.355 --> 00:07:21.565
<i>Lord Jinshi, the palace administrator,</i>

00:07:21.566 --> 00:07:24.568
<i>was trying to reform the rear palace.</i>

00:07:24.569 --> 00:07:26.612
<i>Going against Lord Shishou's way.</i>

00:07:27.655 --> 00:07:29.824
<i>But is that all?</i>

00:07:31.701 --> 00:07:34.077
<i>Shisui. No,</i>

00:07:34.078 --> 00:07:36.372
<i>Loulan mentioned that hairpin
being valuable.</i>

00:07:37.165 --> 00:07:38.249
<i>He's not just an official.</i>

00:07:38.916 --> 00:07:41.377
<i>Not even a eunuch.</i>

00:07:42.086 --> 00:07:43.171
What's wrong?

00:07:44.297 --> 00:07:47.132
When you disguised yourself as an eunuch
to enter the rear palace,

00:07:47.133 --> 00:07:48.759
how were you inspected?

00:07:50.678 --> 00:07:51.596
What? Out of nowhere.

00:07:53.097 --> 00:07:54.891
It was a physical check.

00:07:55.516 --> 00:07:57.477
For a man who's not castrated to enter?

00:07:58.227 --> 00:08:00.188
Three officials perform a physical exam.

00:08:01.063 --> 00:08:03.191
It's hard to fake it.

00:08:04.150 --> 00:08:06.903
<i>Then how did Lord Jinshi get in?</i>

00:08:07.904 --> 00:08:10.197
<i>The only men who can freely come
and go in the rear palace are</i>

00:08:10.198 --> 00:08:12.366
<i>the emperor or his close relatives.</i>

00:08:13.242 --> 00:08:16.870
<i>The only man close to the emperor
is his younger brother</i>

00:08:16.871 --> 00:08:19.581
<i>No, I thought about that possibility,</i>

00:08:19.582 --> 00:08:20.917
<i>but the ages do not match.</i>

00:08:21.584 --> 00:08:24.961
<i>Still, those childish moments of his,</i>

00:08:24.962 --> 00:08:27.423
<i>if that's his real self</i>

00:08:29.258 --> 00:08:30.426
<i>Now that I think of it,</i>

00:08:31.385 --> 00:08:35.473
<i>during the hunt,
he tried to tell me something important.</i>

00:08:36.724 --> 00:08:38.642
<i>Ox bezoar can drive people mad.</i>

00:08:38.643 --> 00:08:40.268
<i>How terrifying.</i>

00:08:40.269 --> 00:08:41.520
What's wrong?

00:08:41.521 --> 00:08:43.064
Nothing.

00:08:45.525 --> 00:08:47.735
<i>All right, let's set this aside for now.</i>

00:08:48.444 --> 00:08:50.738
<i>First, we need to assess the situation.</i>

00:08:54.534 --> 00:08:55.450
Snow.

00:08:55.451 --> 00:08:59.163
Yeah, it's just
beginning to fall in earnest.

00:09:00.081 --> 00:09:01.916
<i>In the north, the highlands?</i>

00:09:02.708 --> 00:09:04.961
<i>Shenmei called it a "Fortress."</i>

00:09:05.670 --> 00:09:08.798
<i>Surrounded by thick walls
and backed by a cliff.</i>

00:09:09.840 --> 00:09:11.801
<i>Why would Shenmei be here?</i>

00:09:13.094 --> 00:09:16.054
<i>Lord Gaoshun suspected the envoy had
snuck out of the inn</i>

00:09:16.055 --> 00:09:19.058
<i>and was dealing with someone.</i>

00:09:19.892 --> 00:09:24.313
<i>Those Western weapons
made in the workshop, the Feifa.</i>

00:09:25.898 --> 00:09:28.317
Are you planning to start a war?

00:09:34.407 --> 00:09:36.617
That's not my decision to make.

00:09:39.954 --> 00:09:41.913
But since Lady Loulan said that,

00:09:41.914 --> 00:09:44.165
go ahead and pretend
to mix some medicines.

00:09:44.166 --> 00:09:45.751
I was going to anyway.

00:09:46.544 --> 00:09:48.336
I will bring you meals.

00:09:48.337 --> 00:09:52.174
Just make sure not to upset Lady Shenmei.

00:09:56.095 --> 00:09:59.431
War, huh. That's bold.

00:09:59.432 --> 00:10:01.684
Now, what do I do?

00:10:02.685 --> 00:10:04.144
<i>We're on the third floor.</i>

00:10:04.145 --> 00:10:05.729
<i>It's snowing outside,</i>

00:10:05.730 --> 00:10:08.649
<i>and even if I escape, I might
collapse before reaching a village.</i>

00:10:09.942 --> 00:10:13.821
<i>Was the last apothecary
confined like this too?</i>

00:10:14.405 --> 00:10:17.366
<i>Supposedly died while testing medicines.</i>

00:10:19.160 --> 00:10:21.077
Oh? Whoa!

00:10:21.078 --> 00:10:24.832
A treasure trove
left by the previous apothecary?

00:10:33.883 --> 00:10:36.636
It must be the post-harvest season by now.

00:10:37.178 --> 00:10:38.386
I remember

00:10:38.387 --> 00:10:41.807
hearing wars happen
when farmers have free time.

00:10:42.767 --> 00:10:44.935
If this is the northern Shihoku province...

00:10:45.519 --> 00:10:47.812
<i>Ten days by boat from the rear palace,</i>

00:10:47.813 --> 00:10:51.984
<i>then walking to the hot springs,
then by carriage.</i>

00:10:52.568 --> 00:10:54.945
<i>There's only one mountainous region
within that range.</i>

00:10:55.863 --> 00:10:59.116
I should've studied more.

00:10:59.742 --> 00:11:02.952
Young master, do not play over there!

00:11:02.953 --> 00:11:04.579
Eh,

00:11:04.580 --> 00:11:07.875
but I haven't finished
exploring that part yet!

00:11:09.377 --> 00:11:12.088
<i>So there's another child besides Kyou-u.</i>

00:11:14.048 --> 00:11:16.424
<i>When we were brought here
from the village,</i>

00:11:16.425 --> 00:11:17.927
<i>Suirei looked reluctant</i>

00:11:18.552 --> 00:11:21.054
<i>when Kyou-u insisted on coming.</i>

00:11:21.055 --> 00:11:23.933
<i>Maybe she really wanted to
leave him behind.</i>

00:11:24.809 --> 00:11:27.978
<i>If the Shi clan starts a rebellion,</i>

00:11:28.729 --> 00:11:31.941
<i>the whole family will be punished.</i>

00:11:32.483 --> 00:11:36.195
<i>Even the women, the children, the babies.</i>

00:11:38.864 --> 00:11:40.950
<i>Do the children know that?</i>

00:11:41.617 --> 00:11:44.286
<i>Have the adults told them?</i>

00:11:47.123 --> 00:11:50.960
I wish I could think of it
as someone else's problem.

00:11:55.297 --> 00:11:56.841
<i>Mother is smiling.</i>

00:12:03.556 --> 00:12:05.349
{\an8}<i>This is where I'm supposed to smile.</i>

00:12:05.975 --> 00:12:08.394
<i>When Mother was mad at Father,</i>

00:12:09.353 --> 00:12:11.105
{\an8}<i>I was supposed to be mad too.</i>

00:12:12.356 --> 00:12:13.899
<i>When she was punishing someone,</i>

00:12:14.733 --> 00:12:17.903
<i>I was supposed to just watch.
That's how I learned to act.</i>

00:12:19.155 --> 00:12:22.825
<i>When Mother smiled, I smiled.
When she grieved, I grieved.</i>

00:12:23.534 --> 00:12:27.037
<i>If I stayed a doll,
Mother would not get angry.</i>

00:12:27.621 --> 00:12:29.457
{\an8}<i>She would not become any uglier.</i>

00:12:30.166 --> 00:12:32.250
{\an8}<i>I felt trapped and suffocated,</i>

00:12:32.251 --> 00:12:34.419
{\an8}<i>but I thought that was fine.</i>

00:12:34.420 --> 00:12:35.671
<i>But then.</i>

00:12:37.047 --> 00:12:38.506
Filthy!

00:12:38.507 --> 00:12:40.925
You and that woman!

00:12:40.926 --> 00:12:43.721
You should never have been born!

00:12:44.221 --> 00:12:45.890
<i>I was wrong.</i>

00:12:46.557 --> 00:12:48.601
<i>Mother just kept getting uglier.</i>

00:12:49.560 --> 00:12:53.689
<i>Even staying a doll could not stop her.</i>

00:13:00.654 --> 00:13:01.614
<i>It was all for nothing.</i>

00:13:03.073 --> 00:13:04.617
<i>By the time I realized that,</i>

00:13:05.451 --> 00:13:07.620
<i>everything was already too late.</i>

00:13:13.667 --> 00:13:14.627
Hey.

00:13:16.128 --> 00:13:18.047
Lady Shenmei is calling.

00:13:20.508 --> 00:13:22.134
I've brought the apothecary.

00:13:22.635 --> 00:13:23.636
Excuse me.

00:13:25.930 --> 00:13:27.640
<i>The smell of musk.</i>

00:13:34.980 --> 00:13:37.107
<i>Something's been mixed in.</i>

00:13:37.733 --> 00:13:38.984
So?

00:13:43.781 --> 00:13:46.408
Is the elixir of immortality ready yet?

00:13:47.034 --> 00:13:48.702
It still needs a bit more time.

00:13:49.453 --> 00:13:50.579
Oh, I see.

00:13:52.665 --> 00:13:54.667
<i>In here, it feels like
they're mistress and servant.</i>

00:13:55.251 --> 00:13:57.377
<i>Even though they usually
seem like close sisters.</i>

00:13:57.378 --> 00:14:00.005
Make sure you have results by tomorrow.

00:14:01.465 --> 00:14:02.466
Understood.

00:14:05.594 --> 00:14:06.595
Let's go.

00:14:07.972 --> 00:14:10.598
<i>I'm only allowed out of the room
once a day,</i>

00:14:10.599 --> 00:14:12.309
<i>during these reports.</i>

00:14:12.810 --> 00:14:14.936
<i>I hate the situation I'm in,</i>

00:14:14.937 --> 00:14:16.689
<i>but not the work itself.</i>

00:14:17.815 --> 00:14:19.607
<i>Most of the medicines are old,</i>

00:14:19.608 --> 00:14:22.652
<i>but the selection is as good
as what the medical office had.</i>

00:14:22.653 --> 00:14:24.946
<i>Tons of research materials too.</i>

00:14:24.947 --> 00:14:28.701
<i>Whoever the last apothecary was,
they must have been incredibly skilled.</i>

00:14:29.702 --> 00:14:31.203
Hey, apothecary.

00:14:34.623 --> 00:14:36.584
Yes, Lord Kyou-u?

00:14:37.543 --> 00:14:38.418
Ugh, gross!

00:14:38.419 --> 00:14:40.962
{\an8}- Ouch.
<i>- Ugh, I want to punch him.</i>

00:14:40.963 --> 00:14:42.422
Who's that?

00:14:42.423 --> 00:14:43.966
The new apothecary.

00:14:44.675 --> 00:14:48.971
Hey, was there another woman
in Lady Shenmei's room?

00:14:49.889 --> 00:14:50.931
Yes, there was.

00:14:51.473 --> 00:14:54.726
Really? My mother's supposed to be there.

00:14:54.727 --> 00:14:55.686
Did she seem well?

00:14:56.437 --> 00:14:57.646
<i>Kyou-u's mother.</i>

00:14:58.522 --> 00:14:59.440
In there.

00:15:02.610 --> 00:15:05.862
I could not say for sure,
I do not know which one she was.

00:15:05.863 --> 00:15:07.364
I see.

00:15:07.990 --> 00:15:09.574
That can't be helped.

00:15:09.575 --> 00:15:12.243
Mother's supposed to be busy with work.

00:15:12.244 --> 00:15:15.080
Maybe I should've just
waited back home after all.

00:15:15.789 --> 00:15:18.166
<i>Was he sent to the hot springs</i>

00:15:18.167 --> 00:15:20.418
<i>to keep him from meeting his mother?</i>

00:15:20.419 --> 00:15:23.255
<i>Or, was it his mother herself.</i>

00:15:24.757 --> 00:15:26.884
Well then, I'll be going.

00:15:29.845 --> 00:15:30.846
Ah, hey.

00:15:37.519 --> 00:15:38.729
Never mind!

00:15:49.782 --> 00:15:51.867
So that's how it is, Lahan.

00:15:52.451 --> 00:15:56.747
Yes, it is just a hypothesis
based on the numbers, but

00:15:57.373 --> 00:16:01.502
<i>The northern fortress governed by Shishou
is being expanded.</i>

00:16:02.002 --> 00:16:05.464
Yes.
It was originally an abandoned fortress.

00:16:06.090 --> 00:16:09.300
No paperwork has been filed
for the expansion.

00:16:09.301 --> 00:16:10.594
In other words,

00:16:11.679 --> 00:16:13.347
rebellion.

00:16:13.973 --> 00:16:17.433
Even if the Shi clan has served
since the Wang Mu's era,

00:16:17.434 --> 00:16:20.228
and even if Shishou was once
the empress regnant's favorite,

00:16:20.229 --> 00:16:22.313
it is still inexcusable.

00:16:22.314 --> 00:16:24.358
How far along is it?

00:16:24.900 --> 00:16:27.861
Judging by when iron prices
started rising,

00:16:28.529 --> 00:16:31.531
I believe preparations are well underway.

00:16:31.532 --> 00:16:33.283
We must act quickly.

00:16:33.867 --> 00:16:36.285
What are you doing,

00:16:36.286 --> 00:16:37.954
Lahan?

00:16:37.955 --> 00:16:40.290
F-Father.

00:16:41.000 --> 00:16:42.167
General.

00:16:42.876 --> 00:16:46.880
It is not proper to visit someone
of that rank so often.

00:16:47.506 --> 00:16:49.591
It invites strange rumors.

00:16:52.219 --> 00:16:53.720
Especially when

00:16:53.721 --> 00:16:57.306
the person in question
does not appear to be male or female.

00:16:57.307 --> 00:16:59.100
- How dare you!
- Basen!

00:16:59.101 --> 00:17:00.144
But Father!

00:17:01.520 --> 00:17:02.604
Lord Gaoshun.

00:17:06.483 --> 00:17:08.902
I understand what the General
is trying to say.

00:17:09.695 --> 00:17:11.904
The fault lies in my own inadequacy.

00:17:11.905 --> 00:17:13.532
Precisely.

00:17:15.034 --> 00:17:17.369
<i>Considering how much he dotes
on his daughter,</i>

00:17:17.870 --> 00:17:19.705
<i>I suppose I'm lucky this confrontation
didn't come sooner.</i>

00:17:20.539 --> 00:17:21.749
<i>The hidden passage,</i>

00:17:22.708 --> 00:17:24.293
<i>the missing eunuch,</i>

00:17:25.044 --> 00:17:27.880
<i>the nonexistent maid "Shisui."</i>

00:17:28.881 --> 00:17:30.965
<i>I was always a step behind.</i>

00:17:30.966 --> 00:17:33.218
<i>And in the end, Maomao was taken.</i>

00:17:34.678 --> 00:17:35.888
<i>That is my failure.</i>

00:17:36.555 --> 00:17:39.724
Despite someone being able to move freely

00:17:39.725 --> 00:17:41.477
between the inner and outer palace,

00:17:42.186 --> 00:17:44.187
my daughter was abducted.

00:17:44.188 --> 00:17:46.731
And that someone

00:17:46.732 --> 00:17:50.152
just sits leisurely
surrounded by paperwork.

00:17:50.736 --> 00:17:52.612
Are you saying

00:17:52.613 --> 00:17:55.783
the fate of one woman
does not matter to you?

00:17:56.575 --> 00:17:58.035
If that is sarcasm, I will accept it.

00:17:58.744 --> 00:18:00.661
But the true enemy is not me.

00:18:00.662 --> 00:18:01.663
It is Shishou.

00:18:03.874 --> 00:18:06.626
If you understand that much,

00:18:06.627 --> 00:18:09.296
then what are you doing?

00:18:10.380 --> 00:18:11.882
Huh!

00:18:13.133 --> 00:18:15.094
<i>The General sees right through me.</i>

00:18:16.053 --> 00:18:19.473
<i>That I lack confidence in my true role,</i>

00:18:20.057 --> 00:18:23.727
<i>that I ran away from it,
and now sit comfortably in this position.</i>

00:18:24.978 --> 00:18:26.772
Half-hearted appearance,

00:18:27.481 --> 00:18:29.274
half-hearted work.

00:18:29.983 --> 00:18:32.861
Do you really think
things will go well like that?

00:18:37.616 --> 00:18:41.120
Remaining an irresponsible damn eunuch.

00:18:41.703 --> 00:18:43.747
What do you think
you can accomplish like that?

00:18:52.339 --> 00:18:53.549
{\an8}I...

00:18:54.591 --> 00:18:56.760
{\an8}Now, now. That was harsh.

00:18:58.804 --> 00:19:00.556
Uncle?

00:19:07.896 --> 00:19:12.358
I never thought you saw me that way.

00:19:12.359 --> 00:19:16.988
I did not choose to become
a eunuch for fun, you know.

00:19:16.989 --> 00:19:19.031
No! That is not what I meant at all!

00:19:19.032 --> 00:19:20.783
I was not talking about you, Uncle!

00:19:20.784 --> 00:19:23.619
I am an irresponsible eunuch.

00:19:23.620 --> 00:19:26.081
I can barely walk properly.

00:19:26.665 --> 00:19:30.543
<i>I even had the luxury of
being carried here in a litter.</i>

00:19:30.544 --> 00:19:33.671
I share the blame for what happened,

00:19:33.672 --> 00:19:38.217
because I failed to keep proper watch
over Maomao.

00:19:38.218 --> 00:19:39.552
That's not true!

00:19:39.553 --> 00:19:42.681
I'm not blaming you at all, Uncle!

00:19:45.601 --> 00:19:46.435
We made it in time.

00:19:47.019 --> 00:19:50.813
When you get angry,
you get aggressive fast.

00:19:50.814 --> 00:19:54.275
But it is important to act
with an awareness

00:19:54.276 --> 00:19:55.818
of the other person's circumstances.

00:19:55.819 --> 00:19:57.945
I know, Uncle.

00:19:57.946 --> 00:20:00.698
That was just
a heat-of-the-moment exchange.

00:20:00.699 --> 00:20:04.161
I never really meant what I said.

00:20:04.786 --> 00:20:07.914
<i>I was not exactly exchanging
harsh words, though.</i>

00:20:07.915 --> 00:20:10.541
Before it turns into a real fight,

00:20:10.542 --> 00:20:14.838
shouldn't you express what you really want
to say, and do it properly, with respect?

00:20:47.371 --> 00:20:49.039
I have come to make a request!

00:20:50.082 --> 00:20:52.000
{\an8}To defeat the traitor, Shishou,

00:20:52.709 --> 00:20:54.962
I ask that the army be mobilized!

00:21:04.179 --> 00:21:06.138
It appears the Shi clan

00:21:06.139 --> 00:21:09.184
has been manufacturing a new type of Feifa
for the past few years.

00:21:09.768 --> 00:21:11.895
{\an8}There was an attempted assassination
using one,

00:21:12.562 --> 00:21:15.106
and also the matter of Loulan's escape.

00:21:15.107 --> 00:21:17.985
{\an8}We already have sufficient proof
of treason.

00:21:18.568 --> 00:21:20.570
{\an8}The rot should be cut out
before it spreads.

00:21:22.864 --> 00:21:27.077
<i>This is not an appeal
to Jinshi the eunuch.</i>

00:21:28.328 --> 00:21:31.832
<i>If Shishou is to be punished for treason
against the nation,</i>

00:21:32.666 --> 00:21:34.333
<i>then it falls to the Imperial Guard,</i>

00:21:34.334 --> 00:21:38.045
<i>the Emperor's direct forces, to act.</i>

00:21:38.046 --> 00:21:39.088
LI

00:21:39.089 --> 00:21:41.008
<i>And the one to lead them</i>

00:21:42.175 --> 00:21:44.303
<i>will not be General Lakan.</i>

00:21:45.012 --> 00:21:46.138
How long?

00:21:46.930 --> 00:21:50.600
How long do you intend to keep deceiving
everyone with that false persona?

00:21:51.476 --> 00:21:52.853
Lord Jinshi.

00:21:53.437 --> 00:21:54.354
No.

00:21:55.105 --> 00:21:56.690
The Moon Prince.

00:21:59.943 --> 00:22:01.445
<i>I always knew,</i>

00:22:02.321 --> 00:22:04.197
<i>this day would come.</i>

00:22:12.122 --> 00:22:14.541
<i>It seems the time has come
to make my decision.</i>

00:23:46.049 --> 00:23:50.470
PREVIEW OF THE NEXT EPISODE

00:23:57.435 --> 00:24:00.062
{\an8}<i>The next episode is "The Toad Tray."</i>

00:24:00.063 --> 00:24:01.815
{\an8}Subtitle translation by:
Abhishek Chand Ramola

